de.mdelab.comparch

Interface MethodSpecification

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArchitecturalElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MethodSpecificationImpl

    public interface MethodSpecification
extends ArchitecturalElement
    A representation of the model object 'Method Specification'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Signature
    • Interface Type
    • Exceptions
    • Performance Stats
    See Also:
    ComparchPackage.getMethodSpecification()
